				<li id="16444887" class="cmnt-root" data="119" data-d="1646370950000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t578600/Lost-Ashes-of-War" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">04 Mar 2022 00:15</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16444887" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">It seems people either have not played the game yet, or don&apos;t understand how Ashes work.  <br/>You can move ashes between weapons freely, they don&apos;t use up and they don&apos;t get soulbound to a weapon.  <br/>You can do this at any Grace site as well as the smith.<br/>You use this item to give yourself TWO of a specific Ash of War so you could have it on two weapons at the same time, without having to move it between them. <br/>You can equip Ashes of War on the weapon without enhancing the weapon stats by selecting the correct option after equipping an Ash of War<br/>You can unequip or move an Ash of War to another weapon at any time.  Simply go to a weapon you want to unequip from.  <br/>You don&apos;t need to unequip Ashes of War to move them to another weapon, you can simply go to weapon you want them on, select them, and select yes when prompted &quot;it&apos;s equipped on X weapon, do you want to unequip and move to this weapon&quot;.<br/><br/></p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16444887" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16444887" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">4</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>121</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>2</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16444887"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16444887" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16444887"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
